      • title

        public TrackHelper.Screen title(java.lang.String title)
        The title of the action being tracked. It is possible to use slashes / to set one or several categories for this action.
        Parameters:
        title - Example: Help / Feedback will create the Action Feedback in the category Help.
        Returns:
        this object to allow chaining calls
